{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 21:05:34.296798", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission accepted.\n\nSummary of submitted solution:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"leaf_router_0_0\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"host_static_blackhole\"]\n\nRecommended next steps (optional):\n- Collect the additional diagnostic outputs listed in the report (kernel route table, FRR/zebra logs, dmesg/syslog, ip route get, tcpdump on eth8 and pc_0_0) to determine how/when the blackhole was installed.\n- If confirmed that the blackhole is unintended, remove the static blackhole route on leaf_router_0_0 (ip route del blackhole 10.0.0.0/24) and verify that the connected route is installed and host reachability to/from pc_0_0 is restored. Also restart/refresh FRR route installation if needed (zebra restart or \"clear ip route\" actions) and review system logs to find root cause to prevent recurrence.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2637, "output_tokens": 198, "total_tokens": 2835, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2560}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
